body:
### YmsCoreBluetooth

A framework for working with CoreBluetooth. Includes Deanna, an iOS application using YmsCoreBluetooth to communicate with a [TI SensorTag](http://processors.wiki.ti.com/index.php/Bluetooth_SensorTag).
